item.description: Do not donate to the Salvation Army, they are anti-LGBTQIA and anti-veteran. They show up with red buckets ringing a bell. Do not give them a dime. Do not give them any time. ( That means do not harass them.) This group was one of the groups that I was told to reach out to when my wife and I were homeless. They were some of the most rude people we had dealt with during that time. item.title: Give Like Dolly on Giving Tuesday
item.description:
Hello Imgur! I operate an affiliate of The Imagination Library in Kent County, MI, and I have to say I love having Dolly as my boss. She has so much to give, she is amazing, generous, and funny, and The Imagination Library that she built is an life-changing program. She hands out cups of ambition to everyone!
Dolly is a beautiful soul.
When I started an affiliate of The Imagination Library, this is what I envisioned. While Brendan Fraser has not answered my calls (yet), our little library still has done amazing work getting books into the hands of children. Every month, each child in our program gets an age-appropriate book mailed directly to them!
I know the Imgur community is wonderful, kind, and incredibly thoughtful, just like Dolly. Thank you, thank you, thank you to those here on Imgur who have supported me in the past! To date, you have helped us mail over 60,000 books! The books from Dolly Parton's Imagination Library are mailed for free to children and families enrolled in the program. While Dolly covers a lot of overhead to make these books affordable and accessible, the wholesale cost of the books are still paid for by the local affiliates like mine. Please consider supporting your own local Imagination Library affiliate with a donation. For $30, you can support one child for a whole year which gifts them 12 books! You can find your local affiliates here: https://imaginationlibrary.com/usa/find-my-program/ The books are wonderfully diverse, high quality, and age appropriate. For families with young children, you can see if the program is available in your area here: https://imaginationlibrary.com/check-availability/ I currently operate an affiliate in Kent County, MI, and we are trying to expand our coverage to include the entire county. Read more about our efforts in Kent County, MI here: https://earlybirdbooks.org/ This year for Giving Tuesday, we have joined a collective campaigned called Grand Rapids Giving Day. If you are willing to support us and the 40+ nonprofits working together to improve our community, please check out our efforts: https://www.grgivingday.org/ https://give.amawithoutborders.org/fundraiser/6508229 And every day, ask yourself, "What would Dolly do?"

Dog Tax: Nimbus is amazed at how life-like our cut-out of Dolly is! She had a lot to say about it :) Stay weird, Imgur.
